SURAT PAULUS KEPADA

THE EPISTLE OF PAUL

JEMAAT DI GALATIA

TO THE GALATIANS

 

 

Penulis: Rasul Paulus (1:1).

Author: The apostle Paul (1:1).

 

 

Waktu Penulisan: Kira-kira 54 M, selama perjalanan pelayanan kali kedua Paulus setelah melintasi Galatia dan tiba di Korintus (Kis. 18:1, 11).

Time of Writing: Approximately A.D. 54, during Paul's second ministry journey, after traveling through Galatia and arriving in Corinth (Acts 18:1, 11).

 

 

Tempat penulisan: Korintus, ketika Paulus tinggal di sana selama satu setengah tahun (Kis. 18:1-11).

Place of Writing: Corinth, while Paul was there for a year and a half (Acts 18:1-11).

 

 

Penerima: Gereja-gereja di Galatia (1:2).

Recipients: The churches in Galatia (1:2).

 

 

Pokok: Kristus Menggantikan Hukum Taurat Dan Berlawanan dengan Religi dan Tradisi

Subject of Galatians: Christ Replacing the Law and Being versus Religion and Tradition
